# Reserved for the `vadd analyze synth` golden snapshot (AC-5.2).
#
# Holds `rtl/*.v` (Rust codegen output, deterministic),
# `templates_info.json`, `design.json`, `settings.json`, and
# `report_inventory.txt` — the set of HLS report paths produced
# after `tapa analyze synth`.
#
# Populated by `test_cli_golden_vadd_synth` when `tapacc` +
# `vitis_hls` are available. See `parity_test.py` for the snapshot
# contract.
